OL,5, The mother of a black 13-year-old boy  
OL,6, says she feels "betrayed" after he was 
OL,7, surrounded by armed police when his    
OL,8, water pistol was mistaken for a gun.   
OL,10,FThe boy was handcuffed and confronted  
OL,11,Fby marksmen in Hackney, east London, in
OL,12,FJuly, the Alliance for Police          
OL,13,FAccountability (APA) said.             
OL,15,FHis mother says she is "extremely      
OL,16,Fangry" and the incident has been "a    
OL,17,Fdeeply traumatic experience".          
OL,19,FThe Met Police's Det Ch Supt James     
OL,20,FConway apologised for "trauma" caused. 
